Begini.

1807
01:41:36,818 --> 01:41:38,841
Dulu, Anda tinggal
di dekat pusat kota.

1808
01:41:38,841 --> 01:41:42,448
Seluruh area itu sudah tenggelam.

1809
01:41:42,865 --> 01:41:43,867
Saya minta maaf.

1810
01:41:44,513 --> 01:41:46,202
