1828
01:42:29,013 --> 01:42:31,224
Kalian berdua menyebabkan ini?

1829
01:42:31,475 --> 01:42:33,832
Kalian mengubah bentuk dunia?

1830
01:42:36,293 --> 01:42:38,148
Mana mungkin, bodoh?

1831
01:42:38,377 --> 01:42:40,609
Sok hebat itu ada batasnya.

1832
01:42:42,590 --> 01:42:43,633
Lihat.

1833
01:42:43,633 --> 01:42:45,384
Kemarin, aku kencan sama putriku.

1834
01:42:45,633 --> 01:42:48,409
