01:43:20,877 --> 01:43:22,441
Maaf sudah mengganggu.

1850
01:43:22,441 --> 01:43:23,776
Mampirlah lagi.

1851
01:43:24,132 --> 01:43:25,111
Hei.

1852
01:43:26,591 --> 01:43:29,114
Jangan khawatir, anak muda.

1853
