1864
01:44:19,182 --> 01:44:19,955
Begitu.

1865
01:44:20,290 --> 01:44:21,895
Jika aku mengatakan itu

1866
01:44:21,895 --> 01:44:22,833
apa tak masalah?

1867
01:44:54,155 --> 01:44:55,302
<i>Tidak.</i>

1868
01:44:55,302 --> 01:44:56,699
<i>Ternyata memang tidak.</i>

1869
01:44:56,699 --> 01:44:58,180
<i>Hari itu, aku...</i>

1870
01:44:58,180 --> 01:45:01,432
<i>Kami memang
mengubah bentuk dunia.</i>

1871
01:45:02,413 --> 01:45:03,663
<i>Aku sudah memilih.</i>

1872
01:45:03,894 --> 01:45:04,812
<i>Aku memilih dia.</i>

1873
01:45:04,812 --> 01:45:06,228
<i>Aku memilih dunia ini.</i>

1874
01:45:06,228 --> 01:45:07,855
<i>Dan aku memilih hidup di sini.</i>

1875
